Create Decomposition Rules that define the way Order Line Items decompose during runtime. You can add conditions to control when or whether items are decomposed. Set scope to determine how many instances of a Fulfillment Order Line Item are created.

Where: Available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: Launch Product Fulfillment Decomposition Rules from the App Launcher.
